 will be blown on it, and the Shout will be made on it. Thus, send blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15807,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/wudu-friday-ghusl-better\/","url_meta":{"origin":25289,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ghusl: Recommendation to bathe on Friday","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah ibn Jundab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever performs ablution on Friday has done well, but whoever performs a ritual bath has done better.\u201d Al-Shafi'i said, \"The command of the Prophet to perform a ritual bath on Friday indicates a preference for\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/special-moment-friday-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":25289,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special moment for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Burdah reported: Abdullah ibn Umar said to me, \u201cHave you heard anything narrated by your father from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, about the special moment on Friday?\u201d I said, \u201cYes. I heard him narrate that the Messenger of Allah said, 'It is the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_cont